<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ny fitiavanao
 No mahagaga anay,
 Ry Zanak'Andriamanitra ô !
 Ry Jeso Tomponay !

[V2]
 Hanavotra aina anay
 No nijalianao,
 Ka famonjena lehibe
 No azonay izao.

[V3]
 Ny mofo sy divay,
 Izay haninay izao,
 Dia mampiseho aminay
 Ny fitiavanao.

[V4]
 Avia, Jeso ô !
 Avia ankehitrio,
 Ka ny fanahinay sasao
 Ho tsara sy madio.

[V5]
 Mampaneke anay
 Hanao ny sitrakao,
 Ka aoka tsy ho tianay
 Izay tsy tianao.

[V6]
 Monena aminay,
 Ry Tompo be fitia !
 Ka aza ilaozanao izahay
 Mandrakizay doria.</lyrics>
<title>Ny fitiavanao FFPM265</title>
<author>Day's Psalter</author>
<hymn_number>265</hymn_number>
</song>